  <h3>What You Can Do</h3>
  <p style="font-family:Trebuchet MS;">Turn your cell phone on "silent"</p>
<p style="font-family:Trebuchet MS;">Completely turn your cell phone off</p>
<p style="font-family:Trebuchet MS;">Put your cell phone out of reach</p>
<p style="font-family:Trebuchet MS;">And if you really can't wait, pull over when you can safely</p>
<h2 style="font-family:Trebuchet MS;">Steps to stop Texting and Driving</h2>
<p style="font-family:Trebuchet MS;">1.Be Aware-know the dangers of texting and driving</p>
<p style="font-family:Trebuchet MS;">2.Commitment-make a lifelong commitment to never text and drive</p>
<p style="font-family:Trebuchet MS;">3.Make it a Habit-create a routine to remind you</p>
<p style="font-family:Trebuchet MS;">4.Influence others-speak up and let others know about the risks</p>
